# LAB HORROR: F-13

## Survival Horror Game in Python & Pygame

---

# Project Overview

Lab Horror: F-13 is a 2D top-down survival horror game developed using Python and Pygame. The player explores an abandoned underground laboratory while being hunted by a dangerous experimental creature known as F-13.

The objective of the game is to survive, explore the laboratory, collect important items, restore power, avoid the monster, and escape the facility.

The project combines horror atmosphere, stealth mechanics, AI behavior, inventory systems, collision detection, animations, and interactive gameplay elements.

